long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Item Manual Tracker allows you to organize and manage your items and their user manuals efficiently. You can store the names of items and attach a URL link to their user manuals for easy access later. It provides a clean interface for adding, searching, and deleting items from your list in just a few clicks.
